        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> (1 comment)\n\n Hi Jim, you're right, it has been a decision on last Friday daily to go with the same version for all policy projets.\n\nSnakeYAML backward compatibility has been broken in v1.20 and fixed in v1.22.\n1.24 is the last released version.\n\nThe change would be applied to following repos :\n    * apex-pdp\n    * api\n    * common\n    * distribution\n    * docker\n    * drools-applications\n    * drools-pdp\n    * engine\n    * models\n    * pap\n    * xacml-pdp\n\nTo validate the change, all these repos has been loaded locally to unit tested successfully.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
